{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">EPB-MQ24</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$18.50 – $21.13 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">20</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">5 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">20</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$21.13 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">100</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$20.20 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">250</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$19.63 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$19.07 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">1000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$18.50 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>- 10,000mAh power bank provides reliable power to keep devices charged throughout the day\n- Built-in USB-C and 5-pin cables for seamless and hassle-free charging of multiple devices, including older iOS devices\n- Power Delivery (PD) technology, ensuring devices and power bank charge quickly and efficiently\n- Built-in USB-C Cable supports both input and output. Can be used to charge the power bank or charge smart devices without needing an additional cable.\n- USB and built-in 5 pin is output only, used to charge the device.\n- LED display shows real-time battery status updates\n- Slim design easily fits into a bag or pocket, making it perfect for on-the-go use\n- UL Certified Lithium-Ion Battery\n- FCC certified\n\n&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt;\n\n       - Built-in USB-C Cable: 5V/3A 9V/2.22A 12V/1.67A\n       - Built-in 5pin Cable: 5V/2.4A 9V/2.22A\n       - USB Port: 5V/2A 9V/2A 12V/1.5A\n\n&lt;b&gt;Input: &lt;/b&gt;\n\n       - Built-in USB-C Cable: 5V/3A 9V/2A 12V/1.5A\n       - USB-C Port: 5V/3A 9V/2A 12V/1.5A</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p